**λ-667 | ##2277a8|Naz##:**  Branding means a lot, nowadays.

**Ω-33 | ##a82222|Pacific##:** Yeah, but these are demons. Their brand is being evil and stealing souls.

**λ-667 | ##2277a8|Naz##:** Is that racist?

**Ω-33 | ##a82222|Pacific##:** It's like their whole thing!

**Ω-33 | ##a82222|Atlantic##:** Oh come //on//, I can provide twenty examples off the top of my head that disprove--

