**Unknown:** You could have knocked first. After the whole thing with Pluto, I'd rather not get into a skirmish.

**Ω-33 | ##a82222|Atlantic##:** ...Are you another god?

**Unknown:** I am. You can call me Fortuna. Shouldn't be too hard to figure out what I'm the goddess of.

**Ω-33 | ##a82222|Atlantic##:** Could-- can you look at us? Kinda weird that you're staring off into space.

**Fortuna:** I am blind.

**Ω-33 | ##a82222|Atlantic##:** Oh. Sorry.

**Ω-33 | ##2277a8|Arctic##:** Nice one, dickweed.

//(Glasses of red wine manifest in the agents' hands.)//

**Ω-33 | ##2277a8|Arctic##:** Man, you are way nicer than Pluto was.

