**Ω-33 | ##a82222|Atlantic##:** How do we get her out of here?

**Ω-33 | ##a82222|Pacific##:** We can't bet it on blackjack again. That's kind of a one-trick pony.

**λ-667 | ##2277a8|Naz##:** How about we just ask her to leave? Occam's Razor and all that.

**Ω-33 | ##a82222|Pacific##:** That'll--

**Fortuna:** If I could intrude on your wonderful meeting, I'll just clear this up. I can't leave Las Vegas unless you're willing to suffer a calamity.

**Ω-33 | ##a82222|Atlantic##:** That's a bit drastic.

