**Ω-33 | ##a82222|Pacific##:** Wait, wait. If you're fine here, why do you need Marks to work for you?

**Fortuna:** It's fun to have a pet. I just gave him a little assistance and he took off by himself. Do you get something out of watering a flower to watch it blossom?

**Ω-33 | ##a82222|Atlantic##:** If we decide to lock him in a cell, will you be upset?

