**Ω-33 | ##a82222|Atlantic##:** Don't you like success?

**Fortuna:** I like success //against the odds//. Winning when the entire hand is stacked against you. Coming in with a dollar and turning it into a fortune.

**Ω-33 | ##a82222|Atlantic##:** Huh.

//(The team huddles again.)//

**Ω-33 | ##a82222|Atlantic##:** I have an idea.

**λ-667 | ##2277a8|Naz##:** What is it?

**Ω-33 | ##a82222|Atlantic##:** Just trust me.

**Ω-33 | ##a82222|Pacific##:** Against all my better judgment, okay.

**Fortuna:** Mm, this should be interesting.

